  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sports & Recreation Manager",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking an experienced and energetic Sports & Recreation Manager to lead the Club’s sports, fitness\nand recreation offering. This role is responsible for creating a vibrant lifestyle experience across all sports facilities, with the fitness centre at the heart of member engagement.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver a dynamic and inclusive sports and fitness experience across all facilities.</li><li>Drive member engagement through programmes, activations, coaching and Club events.</li><li>Oversee daily operations of sports facilities including the gym, pool and courts.</li><li>Ensure facilities are safe, well-maintained and compliant with health and safety standards.</li><li>Develop and manage sports programmes, coaching schedules and major sporting events.</li><li>Manage departmental budgets, financial performance and revenue-generating initiatives.</li><li>Lead, train and motivate sports and recreation staff to deliver high service standards.</li><li>Liaise with the Sports Committee and manage member communications and feedback.</li><li>Collaborate with Marketing and F&B teams to promote sports activities and enhance member experiences.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess at least a Diploma in Sports Science & Management or equivalent and with at least 5 years’ relevant working experience </li><li>Experience managing sports facilities or programmes.</li><li>Strong leadership, organisational, and communication skills.</li><li>Member-focused, proactive and results-driven approach</li><li>Able to work on weekends and public holidays</li></ul><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em><br /></p><p>Enjoy a wide range of benefits when you join our vibrant team:</p><ul><li>Flexible benefits up to $1000.00</li><li>13-month AWS and performance bonus</li><li>Healthcare coverage</li><li>Comprehensive leave schemes</li><li>Transport to/from Sixth Avenue MRT</li><li>Duty meals</li></ul>",
